      "briefing_html": "--- Amarr (2025) ---<br>The Sisters of EVE have requested that we turn Dagan to their forces as payment for their aid. They're welcome to him. The Sisters may appear peaceful, but we are providing this Society member no mercy by delivering him to their care.<br><br>A Sisters of EVE convoy awaits the deliver of Dagan. They wish you to do the honors. I can think of no one more appropriate.<br><br>--- Caldari (old 2010) ---<br>The Sisters of Eve have asked for Dagan himself as payment for their intelligence. The State pays all its debts. A Sisters of Eve ship awaits his delivery. Sister Alitura demands that only you approach the Sisters ship with Dagan. I see no more fitting way to end this.<br>\n<br>\n<br>",
